<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <!-- 上述3个meta标签*必须*放在最前面，任何其他内容都*必须*跟随其后！ -->
    <meta name="keywords" content="孟烦了">
    <meta name="description" itemprop="description" content=" - 孟烦了的个人博客，是一个分享工作经验和生活,值得大家收藏的原创博客网站。">
    <meta name="author" content="">
    <link rel="icon" href="/img/favicon.png">
    <title>孟烦了的独立博客</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap core CSS -->
    <link href="/lib/bootstrap/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- IE10 viewport hack for Surface/desktop Windows 8 bug -->
    <link href="/lib/bootstrap/ie10-viewport-bug-workaround.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- HTML5 shim and Respond.js for IE8 support of HTML5 elements and media queries -->
    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
    <script src="https://cdn.bootcss.com/html5shiv/3.7.3/html5shiv.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.bootcss.com/respond.js/1.4.2/respond.min.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/font/iconfont.css">
    <link href="/lib/markdown/markdown.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/lib/highlight/monokai-sublime.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/details.css">
</head>
<body>
<!--<div class="header-box" style="background-image: url('/img/bg_cover.jpg')">-->
<div class="header-box" style="background-image: url('<%= blogList.imgUrl%>')">
    <div class="header-box-centent">
        <a href="/" class="goHome">HOME</a>
        <div class="header-box-title">
            <p><%= blogList.title %></p>
            <div><span><%= blogList.createTime %></span> <span>@ 孟烦了~</span></div>
        </div>
        <a href="/blog/label/<%= blogList.labelId %>" class="category"><%= blogList.label %></a>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="content-box">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 markdown" id="showdown"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div id="showdownContent" style="display: none"><%= blogList.content%></div>
<footer class="footer-box">
    <div class="footer-box-other">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="footer-box-title">
                        孟烦了的独立博客
                    </div>
                    <div class="footer-box-info">
                        也许是一路上千万种选择，至以博客的诞生。借此在漫漫的长河中，愿与各位时间的朋友结缘。
                        分享孟烦了在前端、nodeJS、web中的各种点滴。纵有千种风情，更欲与君同！
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div class="footer-box-title">
                        相关链接
                    </div>
                    <div class="footer-box-link">
                        <a href="#">技术分享</a>
                        <a href="#">心情随笔</a>
                        <a href="#">英雄榜</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div class="footer-box-title">
                        友情链接
                    </div>
                    <div class="footer-box-link">
                        <a href="#">亚梅</a>
                        <a href="#">飞跃</a>
                        <a href="#">二狗</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="footer-box-me">
                        <a href="#"><i class="iconfont icon-weibo"></i></a>
                        <a href="#"><i class="iconfont icon-weixin "></i></a>
                        <a href="#"><i class="iconfont icon-github3"></i></a>
                        <a href="#"><i class="iconfont icon-youxiang"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-box-copyright">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12">
                <div class="footer-box-copyright--info">
                    <p>design & code by @孟烦了,base on koa2 + mongoDB</p>
                    <p>孟烦了的独立博客© 2018-2019 • All rights reserved.</p>
                    <p>感谢七牛云存储提供静态资源空间，阿里云提供的优质云服务。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>
<script src="/lib/jq/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script src="/lib/bootstrap/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
<!-- IE10 viewport hack for Surface/desktop Windows 8 bug -->
<script src="/lib/bootstrap/ie10-viewport-bug-workaround.js"></script>
<script src="/lib/markdown/marked.min.js"></script>
<script src="/lib/highlight/highlight.pack.js"></script>
<script>
    $(function () {
        /**
         * html转化函数
         */
        $("#showdown").html(marked($("#showdownContent").text()));
        $("#showdownContent").remove();
        hljs.initHighlightingOnLoad();
    });
</script>
</body>
</html>